These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: lavender, emerald, mauve, purple, lilac
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, december, march, january, april
There 5 different types of food: strawberry, lettuce, blueberry, tomato, garlic
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person who likes mauve is the person who likes mauve##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 6. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 7. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
 8. the person who likes purple is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
10. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person who likes lilac is between the person eating lettuce and the person who's birthday is in april##2
12. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
13. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Color      | lavender        | emerald | lilac     | mauve   | purple |
| Birthday   | march     | december      | january | april   | may    |
| Food   | tomato  | lettuce     | strawberry | blueberry | garlic  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

