.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, spy, western, fantasy, musical
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, game, old-henry, chaman, blend
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, badminton, water-polo, tennis, sailing
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, skateboard
 1. the person driving the skateboard is in the middle##1
 2. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 3. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the blend-smoker##2
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person watching spy movies##1
 7. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is the chaman-smoker##1
 9. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person watching western movies##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Movie-Genre         | fantasy | adventure | musical    | spy  | western    |
| Cigar   | blend    | game       | old-henry      | pall-mall | chaman        |
| Sport   | sailing   | badminton     | lacrosse    | tennis  | water-polo     |
| Transport     | roller    | quad-bike | skateboard | scooter | helicopter |

