.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: tea, almond-milk, sprite, hot-chocolate, juice
The people have 5 different jobs:  freelancer, dancer, police-officer, fisherman, designer
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, gospel, metal, pop, reggae
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, amaryllis, orchid, poppy, daffodil
 1. the person drinking juice is the fan of gospel##1
 2. the person who growspoppy is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of pop is in the middle##1
 4. the freelancer is in the middle##1
 5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 7. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
 8. the freelancer is on the right of the dancer##1
 9. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
10. the person who growssunflower is the fisherman##1
11. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
13. the person who growsdaffodil is between the designer and the person drinking sprite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Beverage         | tea | juice     | sprite   | almond-milk   | hot-chocolate |
| Job   | designer  | dancer | freelancer | fisherman | police-officer        |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | gospel      | pop       | reggae       | ambient       |
| Flower         | amaryllis | daffodil  | poppy    | sunflower    | orchid        |

