.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: apricot, red, pink, blue, fuchsia
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, aristoff, dannemann, swisher, cain
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, adventure, drama, disaster, spy
There are 5 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, japanese, pakistani
 1. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 2. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 3. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 4. the pakistani is between the person watching disaster movies and the person who likes blue##2
 5. the person who likes red is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 6. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the indonesian##1
 7. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
 8. the cain-smoker is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching spy movies is in the middle##1
10. the person watching disaster movies is the british##1
11. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
12. the british is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
13. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Color          | fuchsia  | pink     | blue   | red     | apricot |
| Cigar         | cain | dunhill    | dannemann  | swisher | aristoff   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure        | scientific    | spy     | drama     | disaster    |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | indonesian | japanese | pakistani | british   |

