.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
5 different pets are kept: hamster, goat, lizard, mouse, frog
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, prince, cain, bongani, davidoff
5 different games are played: domino, billiard, chess, backgammon, poker
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: climbing, parkour, skateboarding, volleyball, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 2. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the owner of the lizard is between the person who's sport is parkour and the baccarat-smoker##2
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 8. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 9. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
10. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person playing domino##1
11. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
12. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing domino##1
13. the cain-smoker is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Pet   | mouse       | frog       | hamster   | lizard      | goat    |
| Cigar       | davidoff | bongani        | baccarat       | cain       | prince |
| Game        | poker     | billiard        | backgammon | domino        | chess  |
| Sport      | volleyball | skateboarding | climbing      | weightlifting | parkour  |

