 3. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 4. the wooden house is on the right of the analyst##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 6. the gothic-revival house is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who's sport is baseball##2
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the lawyer##1
 8. the entrepreneur is on the far right##1
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the analyst##1
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
11. the person who growszinnia is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who's sport is baseball##2
12. the cottage house is on the right of the architect##1
13. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
