5 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, horse, pony, rat
There 5 different types of food: eggplant, pear, avocado, lemon, strawberry
 1. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 2. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
 3. the owner of the rat is the person eating pear##1
 4. the owner of the horse is between the person watching zombie movies and the person drinking cola##2
 5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is in the middle##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the person drinking milk##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the owner of the dog is the person watching animation movies##1
13. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |     4      |      5       |
| Movie-Genre         | animation   | crime | epic  | adventure | zombie |
