 4. the person drinking water is the italian##1
 5. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the italian##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the polish##1
 7. the italian is on the left of the person eating kale##1
 8. the person drinking cola is the person traveling to london##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is on the far left##1
10. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the french##1
11. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person drinking cola and the person eating broccoli##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
13. the person eating carrot is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |    5    |
