.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice, mirinda, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, march, august, june, october
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, martial-arts, family, thriller, romance
House: modern, cottage, townhouse, farmhouse, tower
 1. the person watching romance movies is between the cottage house and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
 2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 5. the cottage house is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the cottage house##1
 7. the modern house is on the right of the tower house##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
11. the townhouse house is between the person watching family movies and the person who's birthday is in august##2
12. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage    | juice       | mirinda    | soy-milk | iced-tea  | 7up        |
| Birthday       | october | april | august  | june | march    |
| Movie-Genre       | family        | thriller   | martial-arts  | romance   | scientific |
| House   | farmhouse       | townhouse      | tower      | modern | cottage  |

