.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
House: craftsman, modern, art-deco, townhouse, ranch-style
5 different games are played: monopoly, go, scrabble, whist, bridge
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
5 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, bird, snake, dog
 1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the person playing whist is between the person watching crime movies and the person playing scrabble##2
 3. the townhouse house is the person playing whist##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the townhouse house is between the person playing bridge and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 7. the owner of the snake is the art-deco house##1
 8. the craftsman house is the owner of the bird##1
 9. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
10. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the person playing scrabble is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| House      | craftsman      | modern         | townhouse      | art-deco | ranch-style     |
| Game           | go | scrabble | whist | bridge    | monopoly  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| Pet   | bird  | chinchilla        | mouse   | snake    | dog     |

