.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: folkd-games, chess, photography, puzzles, skydiving
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, davidoff, baccarat, chaman, blend
The people have 5 different jobs:  police-officer, musician, software-developer, firefighter, bartender
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: reggae, folk, country, pop, soul
 1. the bartender is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 2. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
 3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 4. the fan of country is on the far left##1
 5. the musician is between the fonseca-smoker and the police-officer##2
 6. the fonseca-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the fan of reggae and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is folkd-games##2
 9. the firefighter is on the left of the person who's hobby is folkd-games##1
10. the person who's hobby is folkd-games is on the right of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |     4      |     5      |
| Hobby         | skydiving  | photography | puzzles   | chess      | folkd-games |
| Cigar   | fonseca   | chaman    | davidoff | blend | baccarat      |
| Job           | software-developer | musician    | police-officer       | firefighter     | bartender      |
| Music-Genre     | country | soul        | reggae  | folk        | pop    |

