.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, hiking, reading, lilac-climbing, skydiving
5 different pets are kept: horse, turtle, guinea-pig, fish, snake
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, emerald, amber, turquise, lilac
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, ritmeester, baccarat, pall-mall, blend
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 2. the owner of the snake is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person who likes lilac##2
 3. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 4. the owner of the snake is the person who likes ebony##1
 5. the person who likes ebony is between the blend-smoker and the person who likes amber##2
 6. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who likes turquise##1
 8. the person who's hobby is lilac-climbing is the person who likes emerald##1
 9. the havana-smoker is the person who likes emerald##1
10. the person who's hobby is lilac-climbing is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
11. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
12. the owner of the turtle is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking  | cooking      | lilac-climbing |
| Pet   | turtle    | snake   | fish | guinea-pig | horse   |
| Color   | amber | ebony    | lilac    | turquise       | emerald         |
| Cigar   | pall-mall  | ritmeester | blend    | baccarat     | havana      |

 